item.title: Getting started with visual-studio-2015
item.description: Installation/Setup # You can get the download link for the setup file in here : https://www.visualstudio.com [Scroll to the bottom of the page and download the Visual Studio] The setups are relatively simply and common. But do take note when they ask you to download the default or custom, you can choose to download the custom and pick whichever programming language you want to download alongside with it too! [Default mainly comes with C#/VB]
